PositionAlpha: Blend the translational effect of this solver on/off. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
PositionPositiveX: Multiply the POSITIVE X translation. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
PositionNegativeX: Multiply the NEGATIVE X translation. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
PositionPositiveY: Multiply the POSITIVE Y translation. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
PositionNegativeY: Multiply the NEGATIVE Y translation. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
PositionPositiveZ: Multiply the POSITIVE Z translation. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
PositionNegativeZ: Multiply the NEGATIVE Z translation. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
RotationAlpha: Blend the total rotational effect on/off. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
RotateXAlpha: Blend the X-axis rotational effect on/off. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
RotateYAlpha: Blend the Y-axis rotational effect on/off. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
RotateZAlpha: Blend the Z-axis rotational effect on/off. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
